&lt;li&gt;Review SOP’s and identify process gaps based on empirical data analysis; improve and simplify processes, drive standardization, and track teams’ adherence to best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive system automation and data integrity to enhance scalable processes; leverage this foundation to take on progressively broader responsibilities in FP&amp;amp;A and strategic finance.&lt;/li&gt;
