&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced CDL Class-A Driver ready to drive the future of trucking? Join us at Aurora, where your skills and expertise will help shape a safer, more efficient transportation ecosystem. As part of our team, you’ll be at the forefront of autonomous vehicle technology, delivering critical data to our engineers and playing a vital role in testing and refining our cutting-edge systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Safely operate autonomous semi trucks on road and closed courses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide real-time feedback on the Aurora Driver’s performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally to support the evolution of self-driving tech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of commercial driving experience, clean record, and an Interstate Class-A CDL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communicator, strategic thinker, and tech-savvy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Pay&lt;/strong&gt; with opportunities for overtime after 40 hours a week, a possible 10% shift differential, plus company stock options!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comprehensive Health, Dental, and Vision&lt;/strong&gt; coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Time Off&lt;/strong&gt; for a balanced work-life schedule, 20 vacation days and unlimited sick time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Home Time&lt;/strong&gt; - enjoy the stability of a full-time role with regular home time, complemented by occasional overnight trips with travel expenses paid.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meals &amp;amp; Snacks&lt;/strong&gt; - catered lunches daily; snacks and fully stocked fridges at each location or options to order lunch and be reimbursed by Aurora.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
