&lt;li&gt;Perform FPGA development including HDL development, simulation, high-speed digital design, algorithm development, verification, synthesis, and timing analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan, develop, and optimize large designs in state-of-the-art, modern FPGA devices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on writing internal specifications related to system architecture&lt;/li&gt;
