&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelors in Computer Engineering, Electrical Engineering, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Field Programmable Gate Array (FPGA) development experience including HDL code development, simulation, test bench development, synthesis, and timing analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Very proficient in HDLs - System Verilog (in particular), VHDL, Verilog&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Very proficient with System Verilog testing environments, methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong embedded system development experience in a microprocessor and FPGA based mixed signal environment such as the Xilinx Zynq platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise with a large FPGA vendor tool chain such as Vivado, Vitis, Quartus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in C / C++.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Digital Signal Processing (DSP) experience in processor or FPGA-based designs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Xilinx/AMD AI Engine development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Camera ISP or&amp;nbsp; DSP application development/design experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in design/development of RTOS firmware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History of using best practices with version control technologies such as git&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with high speed LVDS interfaces for memory, or peripherals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any level may apply&lt;/li&gt;
