&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in IT, software engineering, or solutions architecture in delivering complex, large-scale commercial applications or platform services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in implementing AI/ML technologies, AI agentic workflows, automation platforms and workflow orchestration tools across Enterprise Applications.&lt;/li&gt;
