&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and debug software tools used in manufacturing tests and provisioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closely collaborate with manufacturing and engineering teams to harden and optimize automated manufacturing test procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data management and analysis to track production test performance metrics, prioritize top issues, and drive continuous improvement activities with cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provides technical test support to all local manufacturing areas, locations, and customers as needed.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;B.S. in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, a related field, or equivalent combination of education and experience&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in data collection with electronic test equipment and data-acquisition systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior verification, validation, and testing experience with emphasis on debugging skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication of test status and results, including writing formal test reports/records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in manufacturing test development and sustaining efforts at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read design drawings/wiring schematics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent analytical abilities, technical writing ability, and a comprehensive understanding of problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience programming in Python is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Linux operating systems.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Google Suite, JIRA, JAMA, and GIT.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a fast-paced team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;International travel to CM for on-site bring-up and support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;M.S. in Electrical Engineering, Computer Science, Mechanical Engineering (with mechatronics experience), a related field, or equivalent combination of education and experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with data aggregation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with FMCW LiDAR and/or RF transceivers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with optical system prototyping and characterization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in modern automotive electronics and diagnostic procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
