&lt;li&gt;High technical aptitude with an ability to understand technical designs, software development lifecycle, challenges and risks; ability to work closely with engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in project management; practical familiarity with both Agile and Waterfall methodologies and ability to apply them where best suited.&lt;/li&gt;
