&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in scripting languages (e.g. Python, bash) and query languages (e.g. SQL) with an emphasis around data management for test reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience with autonomous systems (particularly automotive-based)&lt;/li&gt;
