&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Remain alert and attentive while monitoring the Aurora Driver during extended stretches of autonomy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
