&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal, analytical, and oral and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work independently and collaboratively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Critical thinking skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
