&lt;li&gt;Full benefits package including medical, dental, vison, 401K, life insurance, and disability insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work as part of a team that values its members and works together to achieve positive change.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Budderfly is committed to providing equal employment opportunities to all applicants and employees without regard to race, color, creed, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, marital status, citizenship status, age, national origin, ancestry, disability, veteran status, or any other legally protected status, and to affirmatively seek to advance the principles of equal employment opportunity.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We welcome all job seekers, including those with disabilities. If you are a qualified individual with a disability or a disabled veteran, you may request a reasonable accommodation if you are unable or limited in your ability to use or access the Company’s career web page as a result of your disability&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Flexport:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Flexport, we believe global trade can move the human race forward. That’s why it’s our mission to make global commerce so easy there will be more of it. We’re shaping the future of a $10T industry with solutions powered by innovative technology and exceptional people. Today, companies of all sizes—from emerging brands to Fortune 500s—use Flexport technology to move more than $19B of merchandise across 112 countries a year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The recent global supply chain crisis has put Flexport center stage as we continue to play a pivotal role in how goods move around the world. We are proud to have the support of the best investors in the game who believe in our mission, solutions and people. Ready to tackle global challenges that impact business, society, and the environment? Come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Executive (Sales Manager) – S.Korea&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexport is a technology-driven freight forwarding company on a mission to make global trade easy for everyone. By combining logistics expertise with cutting-edge software, we’ve built a unique value proposition that has fueled exponential growth over the past 10 years. Now, we are expanding our presence in Korea.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity for an experienced and well-connected &lt;strong&gt;Sales Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to take the driver’s seat in building and scaling Flexport Korea, growing the business aggressively, and leaving your mark in the market. You will join a high-performing commercial team that is equally excited to grow Flexport’s presence in Korea and solve customer challenges with tech-enabled freight forwarding solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the future!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the growth of &lt;strong&gt;Flexport Korea&lt;/strong&gt; together with your colleagues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and pursue high-potential clients (self-prospected and SDR-generated leads)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult with new clients to understand their supply chain needs and pain points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create value-driven solutions and showcase Flexport’s capabilities through virtual and in-person meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the &lt;strong&gt;full sales cycle&lt;/strong&gt;, from prospecting to closing deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own and achieve personal sales targets&lt;/strong&gt;, approaching them strategically and consistently delivering results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead customer onboarding by coordinating with internal resources and teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a &lt;strong&gt;high-growth, dynamic sales team&lt;/strong&gt; with strong focus on culture, performance, and career development&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in a freight forwarding/logistics sales role, with full-cycle sales experience from prospecting to closing deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of the freight forwarding industry and proven track record in logistics sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to &lt;strong&gt;set strategic plans and achieve ambitious individual sales goals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to cold-call prospects where you see opportunities to win&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Account management skills with the ability to create an outstanding client experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong discovery skills to identify client pain points and propose value-added solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast learner with a strong work ethic and ambition to become a &lt;strong&gt;top-performing sales manager in Korea&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in &lt;strong&gt;Korean and English&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’s in It for You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum 15 annual leave days&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lunch stipend: USD 8 per day&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual health check-up&lt;/strong&gt; provided&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insurance coverage via AIA&lt;/strong&gt; (including health insurance)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobile phone reimbursement: USD 40 per month&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Appropriated sales incentive based on the performance achievement&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to global learning programs and career development opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EAP (Employee Assistance Program) and global support resources&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be part of a high-growth, dynamic team and build Flexport’s presence in Korea.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re ready to take on big goals and achieve them strategically, we want to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
