&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CIPP/E, CIPP/US, CIPM, or other IAPP certifications&lt;/strong&gt; strongly preferred.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience leading&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;privacy programs or audits within a high-growth or international company.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent legal, business, and technical judgment, with strong stakeholder management skills.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive, collaborative, and capable of working autonomously and across global teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Legal degree&lt;/li&gt;
