&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Flexport:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Flexport, we believe global trade can move the human race forward. That’s why it’s our mission to make global commerce so easy there will be more of it. We’re shaping the future of a $10T industry with solutions powered by innovative technology and exceptional people. Today, companies of all sizes—from emerging brands to Fortune 500s—use Flexport technology to move more than $19B of merchandise across 112 countries a year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The recent global supply chain crisis has put Flexport center stage as we continue to play a pivotal role in how goods move around the world. We are proud to have the support of the best investors in the game who believe in our mission, solutions and people. Ready to tackle global challenges that impact business, society, and the environment? Come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empower our employees around the globe to do their best work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The People Team at Flexport is a strategic partner in driving business success through our most important asset—our people. We strive to deliver talent strategy, leadership development, and exceptional employee experiences that enable teams to thrive. Guided by our values, we empower our internal clients, build for the long term, act with an entrepreneurial spirit, and simplify complexity to create scalable, high-impact solutions. Above all, we win as a team—collaborating across the organization to help our people grow and perform at their best.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The opportunity:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking a Senior Human Resources Business Partner to provide comprehensive human resources support across our corporate and fulfillment operations. This role serves a wide spectrum of HR functions including employee relations, compliance, and performance management. You&#39;ll support diverse teams from corporate to high-volume warehouse environments, ensuring consistent HR practices while adapting to unique business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee Relations and Talent Management:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct thorough and impartial investigations into employee complaints, grievances, and policy violations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mediate and resolve employee conflicts, promoting a positive and respectful work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document all investigation findings and actions taken, providing guidance on performance management and disciplinary actions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and advise managers on complex employee relations issues across multiple business units&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support performance management processes, including goal setting, reviews, and development planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance &amp;amp; Risk Management:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with employment laws (ADA, FMLA, EEO, OSHA, FLSA) and conduct regular audits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain employee records and update handbooks/policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver compliance and HR training programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audit FLSA requirements including time-tracking and overtime compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HR Support:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze HR metrics to provide data-driven recommendations to leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support organizational change, compensation/benefits analysis, and employee engagement initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead special projects related to culture, diversity &amp;amp; inclusion, and employee experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate exit interviews and analyze turnover trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Streamline and improve HR processes and workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operations Support:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
