&lt;li&gt;High degree of Business Acumen. Able to quickly learn a business and support broader business goals with a People team lens.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in HRIS systems (Workday preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SHRM-CP, PHR, or similar certification preferred&lt;/li&gt;
